<HH> ============= Screen: Sierra's completed chart ======================== </HH>

<Markdown id="filled_out_poster">
## Sierra's Chart

| | Add Something | Remove Something |
|---|---|---|
| **Increase Behavior** | **Positive Reinforcement:** _Give the child a sticker of his favorite cartoon character when he cleans up when asked._ | **Negative Reinforcement:** _Allow the child to have a pass on chores when he cleans up when asked._ |
| **Decrease Behavior** | **Positive Punishment:** _Make the child write "I will clean up my toys" 100 times if he does not clean up when asked._ | **Negative Punishment:** _Take away his electronics for a week after he refuses to clean up three times._ |

Remember:
- **Positive** = Adding something
- **Negative** = Removing something
- **Reinforcement** = Increases behavior
- **Punishment** = Decreases behavior
</Markdown>


