<HH> ============= Screen: The roommate's reply ======================== </HH>

<Markdown id="roommate_response">
## Sierra's sister's email:

Hey!

I just wanted to thank you and your friends for helping me out
with the clean-up situation!

I tried the positive reinforcement technique you all suggested,
and it actually worked!

It took me a while to figure out the perfect reinforcement. He loves
Paw Patrol, so I started giving him a Paw Patrol sticker every time he
put his toys away when I asked. I gave him one sticker for each clean-up
and told him that once he filled a row on his sticker chart, he'd get to
pick the movie for family movie night. 😊

So far, he has cleaned up without a fuss three days in a row!

Please tell everyone I really appreciate their ideas! Y'all are lifesavers!
</Markdown>


